## ⚡ Quick Start

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/effjy/axis.git
cd axis

# Build (requires libsodium and a Kyber‑1024 library – see Installation)
make

# Run the interactive menu
./axis512

# Encrypt a file (choose option 1)
#  → Enter password, optional PIN, input & output paths.

# Decrypt a file (choose option 2)
#  → Same steps – the original file is restored.
```

Non‑interactive example (feeding commands via stdin):

```bash
./axis512 --quiet --kyber <<< "1
my_password
0
secret.docx
secret.axis
"
```

